thread.title: BRIEF-Zhejiang Jindun Fans' 11 Banks Accounts Are Frozen As Of Feb 13

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Zhejiang Jindun Fans' 11 Banks Accounts Are Frozen As Of Feb 13

organizations.name: reuters) - zhejiang jindun fans co ltd

text:
Feb 12 (Reuters) - Zhejiang Jindun Fans Co Ltd:
* SAYS ITS 11 BANKS ACCOUNTS ARE FROZEN AS OF FEB 13, ACTUAL ACCOUNT BALANCE IN THE FROZEN ACCOUNTS ARE ABOUT 37.9 MILLION YUAN ($5.99 million) Source text in Chinese: bit.ly/2H8YPJB Further company coverage: ($1 = 6.3258 Chinese yuan renminbi) (Reporting by Hong Kong newsroom)
